<noinclude>
This template was generated by the following Python code, assuming <code>credits.json</code> is the ''Java'' or ''Bedrock'' credits file and [https://minecraft.wiki/api.php?action=query&prop=transcludedin&pageids=5530&tinamespace=0&tilimit=500&format=json <code>api-result.json</code> from this query] are located in the current directory.

Known names are taken from [[:Special:WhatLinksHere/Template:Infobox person]].

<syntaxhighlight lang="python">
import json

TEMPLATE_START = "{{:Credit_sequence/Credits/Part"
known_names = ["4J Studios"]
credits = []

with open("credits.json", encoding="utf-8") as f:
    credits = json.load(f)

# api-result.json saved from
# https://minecraft.wiki/api.php?action=query&prop=transcludedin&pageids=5530&tinamespace=0&tilimit=500&format=json
with open("api-result.json", encoding="utf-8") as f:
    known_names.extend(i["title"] for i in json.load(f)["query"]["pages"]["5530"]["transcludedin"])

with open("credits.mediawiki", "w", encoding="utf-8") as f:
    f.write("{{collapse|title=<h3>Credits transcript</h3>|content=\n")

    for section in credits:
        s_name = section["section"]
        assert s_name != ""
        f.write(f"{TEMPLATE_START}|section={s_name}|disciplines=\n")

        for discipline in section["disciplines"]:
            d_name = discipline["discipline"] or "no"
            f.write(f"  {TEMPLATE_START}|discipline={d_name}|titles=\n")

            for title in discipline["titles"]:
                t_name = title["title"] or "no"
                f.write(f"    {TEMPLATE_START}|title={t_name}|names=\n")

                for name in title["names"]:
                    match name.split(" (", maxsplit=1):
                        case [name]:
                            if name in known_names:
                                name = f"[[{name}]]"
                        case [name, company]:
                            if name in known_names:
                                name = f"[[{name}]]"
                            name = f"{name} ({company}"  # undo the split
                        case _:
                            raise ValueError("Unexpected")

                    f.write(f"      {TEMPLATE_START}|name={name}}}}}\n")

                f.write("    }}\n")

            f.write("  }}\n")

        f.write("}}\n")

    f.write("}}\n")
</syntaxhighlight>
